{"tid":2138921,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國雷神公司與以色列軍火商簽約 年底於美國設廠生產鐵穹防禦系統","createTime":"2020-08-04T03:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T06:10:10.000Z","uid":28765,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"e8b536e968a6ecd1a3e205739147856ae665d475","tid":2138921,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:06:36.000Z","msg":"美國雷神飛彈與防禦公司近期與以色列拉斐爾先進防禦系統公司（Rafael Advanced Defense Systems）簽署合資企業協議，宣佈將以雷神拉斐爾區域保護系統（Raytheon RAFAEL Area Protection Systems）為名，年底前在美國設廠生產鐵穹防禦系統（Iron Dome Missile Shield）。<br />\n<br />\n據《Defense World》報導，雷神飛彈與防禦公司3日和拉斐爾先進防禦系統公司簽署合資企業協議，宣佈將在美國設廠生產鐵穹防禦系統。新的合資企業將稱之為雷神拉斐爾區域保護系統，預計將在年底前確立設廠位置。<br />\n<br />\n《Defense World》指出，雷神公司陸戰與防空系統高層德內克（Sam Deneke）表示，「這會是以色列以外首個鐵穹防禦系統全彈設施，將幫助美國國防部及其全球盟友取得系統，用以防衛部隊成員以及關鍵基礎設施」。<br />\n<br />\n.......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3249015\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3249015&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O1pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=a493ff7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3249015&h=dcc5e49f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3249015</a>"},{"pid":"0a090e7e81167f0ba862da1d681850b3444ecf08","tid":2138921,"uid":126305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:08:23.000Z","msg":"以色列戰鬥國黎男女都全民皆兵"},{"pid":"e7a5ab0cac1e5ffc90cd3793115bbea5d75f5896","tid":2138921,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:12:12.000Z","msg":"以色列屈機到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0762c42c7a7b42fef23acea7dba552d167da3d1b","tid":2138921,"uid":310914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:12:58.000Z","msg":"57@20股rtx你教我點輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91677c2d8987ecd14db99140c700eec8